s taken as a pet form of   Margaret   or   Margery .  As a male name, it is an altered form of the Continental male name <i>Marian</i>, a derivative of Latin <i>Marianus</i> (from   Marius  ), but is now rarely, if ever, used. It was the birth name of the American film star  John Wayne  (  1907–79 )."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Lady Marion Ogilvy was born in 1510, in Deskford, Banffshire, Scotland, United Kingdom. She had at least 1 daughter with Donald Innes of Lochbroom. She died in 1558, in Kinnell, Angus, Scotland, United Kingdom, at the age of 48."},"et":{"1510–1558":"1510–1558","1502–Male":"1502–Surnud","1532–1571":"1532–1571","1558":"1558","1502":"1502","1510":"1510","1532":"1532","1571":"1571","Deskford, Banffshire, Grampian, Scotland,":"Deskford, Banffshire, Šotimaa, United Kingdom","Balmachy, Midlothian, Scotland":"Midlothian, Scotland","Kinnell, Angus, Scotland":"Kinnell, Angus, Šotimaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1510–1558":"1510–1558","1502–Male":"1502–Kuollut","1532–1571":"1532–1571","1558":"1558","1502":"1502","1510":"1510","1532":"1532","1571":"1571","Deskford, Banffshire, Grampian, Scotland,":"Deskford, Banffshire, Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Balmachy, Midlothian, Scotland":"Midlothian, Scotland","Kinnell, Angus, Scotland":"Kinnell, Angus, Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1510–1558":"1510–1558","1502–Male":"1502–Décédé","1532–1571":"1532–1571","1558":"1558","1502":"1502","1510":"1510","1532":"1532","1571":"1571","Deskford, Banffshire, Grampian, Scotland,":"Deskford, Banffshire, Écosse, Royaume-Uni","Balmachy, Midlothian, Scotland":"Midlothian, Écosse","Kinnell, Angus, Scotland":"Kinnell, Angus, Écosse, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Lady Marion Ogilvy est née en 1510, à Deskford, Banffshire, Écosse, Royaume-Uni. Elle a eu au moins 1 fille avec Donald Innes of Lochbroom. Elle est décédée en 1558, à Kinnell, Angus, Écosse, Royaume-Uni, à l’âge de 48 ans."},"de":{"1510–1558":"1510–1558","1502–Male":"1502–Verstorben","1532–1571":"15